 Step 7 - begin consensus

 Step 7.1 - choose speaker among delegates (validators)
device_16 is speaker: False
device_5 is speaker: False
device_1 is speaker: False
device_8 is speaker: False
device_13 is speaker: True
validator device_13 has been chosen as speaker for the consensus round 0

 Step 7.2 - build candidate block
device_13 - speaker hashing the block...
device_13 - speaker mines a block in 0.09816384315490723 seconds.

 Step 7.3 - propose it to delegates
validator device_13 is propagating its block to validator device_8.
validator device_8 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_13
validator device_13 is propagating its block to validator device_16.
validator device_16 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_13
validator device_13 is propagating its block to validator device_1.
validator device_1 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_13
validator device_13 is propagating its block to validator device_5.
validator device_5 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_13
accept block based on PoA
device_16 - delegate 1/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_13 mined by device_13 has been verified by device_16!
Delegate device_16 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_13.
accept block based on PoA
device_5 - delegate 2/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_13 mined by device_13 has been verified by device_5!
Delegate device_5 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_13.
accept block based on PoA
device_1 - delegate 3/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received

Delegate device_1 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_13.
accept block based on PoA

device device_1 is summing acctacy gains
validator device_1 has aggregated accuracy gains from all the received accuracy gains

 Step 7 - begin consensus

 Step 7.1 - choose speaker among delegates (validators)
device_6 is speaker: False
device_11 is speaker: False
device_16 is speaker: False
device_2 is speaker: True
device_1 is speaker: False
validator device_2 has been chosen as speaker for the consensus round 0

 Step 7.2 - build candidate block
device_2 - speaker hashing the block...
device_2 - speaker mines a block in 0.10183024406433105 seconds.

 Step 7.3 - propose it to delegates
validator device_2 is propagating its block to validator device_6.
validator device_6 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_2
validator device_2 is propagating its block to validator device_16.
validator device_16 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_2
validator device_2 is propagating its block to validator device_1.
validator device_1 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_2
validator device_2 is propagating its block to validator device_11.
validator device_11 has accepted accepted a propagated block from miner device_2
accept block based on PoA
device_6 - delegate 1/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_2 mined by device_2 has been verified by device_6!
Delegate device_6 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_2.
accept block based on PoA
device_11 - delegate 2/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_2 mined by device_2 has been verified by device_11!
Delegate device_11 signed the propagated block proposed by speaker device_2.
accept block based on PoA
device_16 - delegate 3/4 is deciding if a valid propagated block received 
Block accepted from miner device_2 mined by device_2 has been verified by device_16!
